### Create invoice (with optional dueDate)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 100,
    "description": "Test invoice",
    "dueDate": "2026-03-12T12:00:00Z"
}

### Create invoice (without dueDate – no trailing comma)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 100,
    "description": "Test invoice"
}

### Response
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Type: application/json

### Invoices list (default page/limit)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

### Invoices list (page 2, limit 10)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices?page=2&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Invoices list (status filter)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/invoices?status=paid
Content-Type: application/json
